Place meat, squash, pineapple and onions in slow cooker. Top with Simmer Sauce; cover. Cook on LOW 6 to 8 hours (or on HIGH 3 to 4 hours). 15 min. before serving, remove liquid with ladle from slow cooker; set aside. Stir in Finishing Sauce and spinach. Add some of the reserved liquid to desired consistency. Cook, covered, on HIGH 15 min.